    agent-api/apps/dashboard/src/middleware.ts, zakops-agent-api/apps/dashboard/next.config.ts)
  - Removing defaults would break compose that embeds defaults (e.g., DASHBOARD_SERVICE_TOKEN) (zakops-agent-api/deployments/docker/docker-
